OL,3,CAverage water bill to increase by #26
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FThe average household water bill in
OL,7,FJersey will increase by #26 next year.
OL,9,FJersey Water says the rise is in line
OL,10,Fwith inflation and works out at around
OL,11,Fan extra 7p a day.
OL,13,FFrom Wednesday 1 January 2025, tariffs
OL,14,Fwill go up by 5.7%, matching the
OL,15,FRetail Price Index (RPI) from March
OL,16,F2024.
