OL,3,CAverage water bill to increase by #26
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FA similar annual rise has been
OL,7,Fannounced in England and Wales with
OL,8,Fhousehold bills expected to go up by
OL,9,Fan average of #19 for every 12 months
OL,10,Fover the next five years.
OL,12,FThe utility company says the charges
OL,13,Freflect the impact of the current
OL,14,Feconomic climate on its operating
OL,15,Fcosts and the investment it is making
OL,16,Fto "create greater resilience and
OL,17,Fsecurity for the island's future water
OL,18,Fsupply needs".
