OL,3,CAverage water bill to increase by #26
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,FChief Executive of Jersey Water Helier
OL,7,FSmith says: "Acting in the best
OL,8,Finterests of our customers is our
OL,9,Fnumber one priority. We do this by
OL,10,Fbalancing the need to keep bills fair
OL,11,Fand affordable with investing in
OL,12,Fcritical upgrades to our
OL,13,Finfrastructure so that we can continue
OL,14,Fto provide a high-quality, sustainable
OL,15,Fwater supply for customers today and
OL,16,Fin the future.
