OL,3,CAverage water bill to increase by #26
OL,4,Cin Jersey
OL,6,F"Next year, we are still anticipating
OL,7,Fa 3.9% increase in our operating
OL,8,Fcosts, on top of rises in contractor
OL,9,Fcosts for our capital investment
OL,10,Fprogramme and an overall decrease in
OL,11,Fcustomer demand for water."
OL,13,FJersey Water adds it will not make any
OL,14,Ffurther price changes before 2026.
OL,16,FCustomers who may be worried about
OL,17,Ftheir bills can find flexible payment
OL,18,Foptions, advice and apply for free
OL,19,Fwater saving devices through the
OL,20,Fcompany's website here.
